Description: FFI bindings and tools for GnuCash
 rgnucash provides Rust FFI bindings to the libgnucash engine,
 along with extended functionality for business entities, queries,
 and builders.
 .
 Includes:
  * gnucash-app - Command line tool for GnuCash operations
  * librgnucash - Rust bindings to libgnucash
